cast.text:
let's talk about this basic permissionls rewards model

everyone can create a game with degen rewards (or not)

game creator send the rewards to the pool and select max n winners

the first n winners in 24 hours earn a share of the rewards pool

it is so fair that even the game creator can participate in it

there is an admin that can configure some settings like number of words and game duration but with no access to the degen in the pools

just a permissionless word search game with degen rewards

follow me for more easy degenomics rewards systems xd
